{"tid":1054690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"之前試過inbox me，痴線佬真係多到hihi","createTime":"2019-03-10T04:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T05:45:06.000Z","uid":241515,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d632ba154bf13daacdfe765552d7f7016720ef0f","tid":1054690,"uid":241515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"之前喺某個地方試過出inbox me，搵興趣相近嘅人傾計(啱傾嘅再諗啦)，但發現呢個世界啲人真係有啲癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 我都衰嘅，因為驚真係會有騙案或者起底嗰啲，相、ig同電話嗰啲都未比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啱傾嘅傾耐左嘅到時再比啦<br />\n<br />\n痴線佬例子<br />\n1. 癲佬<br />\nA君: 其實我唔明點解啲女仔同意出黎見面，但就告人強奸係咩心態，出得黎見唔係諗住純吹水呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左答謝你嘅坦白，我決定block左你，你講到見面=同意你做咩都得??? 咁我一定會見你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。第一次見面咋wo，男女都同意就冇所謂啫，唔通唔同意你拉佢入後巷都唔可以告強奸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 頭一日傾計<br />\nB君: 聽朝我要早起身啊，你叫醒我啦<br />\n我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB君: 你瞓唔著？bb要唔要我哄你瞓覺<br />\n其實我同你真係未係好熟，好對唔住我真係頂唔順呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申第一次出post嘅毒絲，開始懷疑人生，其實係咪我太唔正常 ...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc84c49d2c741dc230d2b10ea4f547acdea949ad","tid":1054690,"uid":23170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"依個社會一向都係咁，現今只係社會開放左令到人覺得識陌生人好似好正常咁。你返去無internet無app嘅年代，你求其喺條街到同人say hi, 睇下10個入面有幾多個會借啲意拉你入後巷姦左你呀。痴線佬一直無多，只係你多左access去搵到依啲人。"},{"pid":"155be15ce9dfc3e3a57cd88a8f9e8e5b5ff5848e","tid":1054690,"uid":84613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"佢地係痴線，但都係睇下有冇痴線婆對佢地有反應，呢d apps都係少玩為妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3f5055f2931cc6e228e0f219d439e346450e1c","tid":1054690,"uid":241515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc84c49d2c741dc230d2b10ea4f547acdea949ad","tid":1054690,"uid":23170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"依個社會一向都係咁，現今只係社會開放左令到人覺得識陌生人好似好正常咁。你返去無internet無app嘅年代，你求其喺條街到同人say hi, 睇下10個入面有幾多個會借啲意拉你入後巷姦左你呀。痴線佬一直無多，只係你多左access去搵到依啲人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T04:33:15.000Z","msg":"的確，有時見到網上啲罵戰都覺得有啲恐怖🤦🤦🤦 三觀不正嘅人多到呢..."},{"pid":"668ec2f82562361010b01eb2c2e085eca927839a","tid":1054690,"uid":241515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"155be15ce9dfc3e3a57cd88a8f9e8e5b5ff5848e","tid":1054690,"uid":84613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"佢地係痴線，但都係睇下有冇痴線婆對佢地有反應，呢d apps都係少玩為妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"你啱...真係好鬼多癲佬<br />\n不過我番工識唔到人，8成女仔，2成3、40歲左右有家室嘅男性<br />\n加上自己毒 唔出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申係用tg，其實都有正常人嘅，暫時睇落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812fb181555764447aa69d58204aee4b3a0501a1","tid":1054690,"uid":168784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"有個女仔見佢簡介寫 鐘意運動 又做gym 遊水<br />\n問佢係咪好大隻 就block我 好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75ee59f8878620cf843b52293d5c085da4036bc","tid":1054690,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019